          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Petersburg</placeName>
                                        <date>Feby 20" 1848</date>.</p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">would you be<lb/> kind enough to write for me at
                                        your earliest<lb/> convenience an inscription for me to have
                                                  <sic>ins-<lb/>-ribed</sic> on my late Husbands
                                        Tomb stone, both<lb/> in Hebrew and English,</p>
                              <p>You will <sic>recolect</sic> his hebrew name as you<lb/> have
                                        frequently called him up in Synagogue</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">he departed this life on the <date>third<lb/> day
                                                  of June 1847</date>, in the 75" year of his
                                        age<lb/> and when done will you please forward<lb/> the same
                                        by mail to me at this place<lb/> I leave the wording of the
                                        Inscription entirely<lb/> to your superior knowledge with
                                        sentiments<lb/> of regard to self</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">I remain your's</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">very Respectfully c</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">
                                        <persName role="author">Maria Morris</persName>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">
                                        <placeName>Penn</placeName>
                              </p>
